        5,
        26
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1",
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://neptunebeachpreservation.org/"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "City officials met in Wheeler’s train station until a new town hall opened in 1935, turning the old depot into the first municipal office.",
